file: SteeringMessagesProviderInterface.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Contract\\Hook\\SteeringMessagesProviderInterface"
type: interface
summary: Defines the contract for retrieving steering messages within the AgentCore hook system. This interface abstracts the source of configuration or routing directives used to steer agent behavior. It serves as a dependency injection point for components requiring dynamic message resolution.
